<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٢٤٦⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">قال:</span> بسم <span class="c2">(اللَّه)</span> <span class="c2">(٢)</span> و <span class="c2">(السلام)</span> <span class="c2">(٣)</span> على رسول اللَّه، وإذا <span class="c2">(دخل)</span> <span class="c2">(٤)</span> بيتا ليس فيه أحد قال: السلام عليكم <span class="c2">(٥)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
